in=bakanome>Bakanome</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 36<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/28/02 4:05:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1464.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Twinking others is bad</span><hr size=1> I dunno.  I'll never twink myself, but accept things from others if they offer, I don't see why not. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usnoutfv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Snout FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/28/02 8:32:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1464.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Twinking others is bad</span><hr size=1> People pay too much attention to what others are doing, not enough time on what they're doing. The whole twink thing and what &quot;others think about it&quot; is kinda silly.<br>
<br>
Oh, what I think on twinking? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Do what you want. It's a free universe. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>~*~ Snout has spoken. ~*~<BR>
